---
title: Sunday Lentil Stew with Potatoes and Garlic Toast
description: This hearty stew tastes like it has been simmering for hours, but it's done in just 30 min! Sour cream brings a touch of creaminess to this veggie and lentil wonder, while crispy, buttery dill-garlic toast is perfect for dipping.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-lentilles-du-dimanche-9d3aa749.jpg
